{"tid":598997,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撞車黨葵涌出沒戲太屎 駕駛者落車質問　碰瓷男敗走","createTime":"2018-03-20T04:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T05:27:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc3d2c76d1d6c22676c22965c6de49a3c74aeb04","tid":598997,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T04:42:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180320/20337389\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180320%2F20337389&d=D%2BverwI54%2FCFhfeffaWAvgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=89d0af68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180320%2F20337389&h=1b4233e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180320/20337389</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有片：撞車黨葵涌出沒戲太屎<br />\n駕駛者落車質問　碰瓷男敗走 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n中國內地不時出現撞車黨，香港亦出現類似碰瓷事件。有網民近日喺fb群組「香港交通突發報料區」上載車cam片段，顯示喺3月18日凌晨1點幾，當車輛行經葵涌石籬和宜合道時，一名手持一袋物品嘅男子突然飛撲到車頭朝擋風玻璃一撼，繼而高舉雙手，點知駕駛者好霸氣咁落車，不甘示弱咁同呢一個男子理論，最終呢名男子手抱後腦敗走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180320/large/a1403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180320%2Flarge%2Fa1403a.gif&h=5351f682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【撲出】<br />\n碰瓷男手拿大袋物品撲出馬路。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180320/large/a1403b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180320%2Flarge%2Fa1403b.gif&h=dddef161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【攔車】<br />\n掛住一雙大大黑眼圈嘅碰瓷男，頭撼涉事車輛大銀幕，伸開雙手示意唔畀走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180320/large/a1403c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180320%2Flarge%2Fa1403c.gif&h=1174f1ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【敗走】<br />\n司機聯同女乘客落車理論，碰瓷男抱頭敗退。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民︰裝cam最實際<br />\n<br />\n短片可見，呢名疑似撞車黨男子飛撲向車頭後嘅肢體動作好奇怪，上載片段人士就喺帖文指，「大家返葵涌石梨（籬）要小心，開始有呃錢黨」，又留言指，「好在收（油）得到，唔係就大鑊！對司機冇保障」、「po出嚟等大家知道又有呢d事出現！叫大家小心的。段片只係一小段，最後係有阿sir捉咗佢！」<br />\n有人留言話，事發地點約為和宜合道寶星中心對開，唔少網民就話乜都係假，裝車cam最實際，當然唔少人懷疑呢啲橋段可能係內地引入喎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180320/large/a1403d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180320%2Flarge%2Fa1403d.gif&h=1bb1f8e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n識睇 睇留言<br />\n<br />\nVivi Chen：香港交通咁繁忙，咁多車，總會有次弄假成真撞瓜呢啲蛋散，佢就話死不足惜，司機就多得佢唔少！<br />\n<br />\nLee Wai Hang：成功引入專才<br />\n<br />\nDavid Au：應該告佢危害道路駕駛者，唔知有冇呢條罪<br />\n<br />\nEc Chan：最緊要裝車cam<br />\n<br />\nLau Tosrr：呢D演技霞姨都唔會畀飯盒佢<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：《蘋果》網頁"},{"pid":"547651276e79df4eebfc520c6938b5eea10a904b","tid":598997,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:23:22.000Z","msg":"終於睇齊"},{"pid":"f5b88e3fe84b4c671c3dc7edcecba6541eddbdbc","tid":598997,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9dd68e52088d34c652c53c25efaf15a0c14118","tid":598997,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"中港融合、文化交流"},{"pid":"2ed90e41e9bce88e9582b4abf87ba718d6aad271","tid":598997,"uid":50041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:27:32.000Z","msg":"其實係車cam公司銷售手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}